{
  "stem": "8252.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I went back there and my mother was with me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And maybe, I don't know how long after that, they came in.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There was posters all over the city that Jews have to wear a yellow armband.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The Jews are not allowed to cross or be on the main street, which separated the city into two parts.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I was with my mother in that apartment.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I was going around town and fortunately, we had to-- I didn't mind.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I was crossing that street anyhow very fast and so on.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I was everywhere.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And to get money, you know, all I had to do was get into the factory, get a piece of textile goods or something, and take it to the retail store, and I had money.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So this is how we provided for ourselves.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And then one day there is a knock on the door, and there are some German officers.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we're taking this apartment.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "You go out.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "You know, just like this.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "You just go out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Fortunately, that wasn't our apartment.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We could go to our apartment.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "The winter is approaching, and I knew that because it was a factory in the back, we had coal there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "So I will be able to heat during the winter.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I didn't know how long I would be there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Right after they came in, already there were-- there were acts of terrorism and of intimidation of the population.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "One of them was affected me terribly because my best friend's father, who was one of the Jewish Community Council in Lodz, the whole Community Council was taken out and shot and killed.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my friend lost his father like this.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was just the beginning right after they came in.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
